snippet.title: Grateful Every Day (Barron Trump Singing Imagined)
snippet.description:
Grateful Every Day

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
Verse 1
Wake up, sunshine, brand new day,
God is with me, He lights my way!
Through these halls, through every door,
I feel His love, I praise Him more!

Pre-Chorus
Hands up high, heart so free,
God is good, He’s guiding me!
Every step, every prayer,
I see His grace everywhere!

Chorus
Oh, I’m grateful every day! (Hey!)
God is good in every way! (Hey!)
Through the highs, through the lows,
He’s the rock that makes me grow!
Oh, I’m singing loud and strong,
God’s with me, I can’t go wrong!

Verse 2
Mama’s wisdom, Dad’s strong hands,
They taught me how to take a stand.
But through it all, it’s clear to see,
God’s the one who carries me!

Pre-Chorus
Hands up high, heart so free,
God is good, He’s guiding me!
Every step, every prayer,
I see His grace everywhere!

Chorus
Oh, I’m grateful every day! (Hey!)
God is good in every way! (Hey!)
Through the highs, through the lows,
He’s the rock that makes me grow!
Oh, I’m singing loud and strong,
God’s with me, I can’t go wrong!

Bridge
Clap your hands, lift your voice,
Praise the Lord, let’s all rejoice!
Every blessing, every light,
God is shining oh so bright!

Chorus
Oh, I’m grateful every day! (Hey!)
God is good in every way! (Hey!)
Through the highs, through the lows,
He’s the rock that makes me grow!
Oh, I’m singing loud and strong,
God’s with me, I can’t go wrong!

Outro
So I dance, so I praise,
Living in His endless grace!
Grateful, joyful, shining bright,
With God’s love, my heart takes flight!
